---
import { Video, Camera, Instagram, Palette, Lightbulb, Code } from 'lucide-react';
---

<section id="servicios" class="w-full bg-white py-16 sm:py-24 lg:py-32 relative overflow-hidden">
  <!-- Cohete decorativo - Esquina superior derecha -->
  <div class="absolute top-12 right-4 sm:right-8 lg:right-12 z-0 opacity-40 pointer-events-none">
    <img 
      src="/images/cohetes/cohete-primary.svg" 
      alt="" 
      class="w-16 h-16 sm:w-20 sm:h-20 lg:w-24 lg:h-24 transform rotate-12"
      aria-hidden="true"
    />
  </div>

  <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 relative z-10">
    <!-- Badge y Título -->
    <div class="text-center mb-12 sm:mb-16">
      <p class="text-sm sm:text-base font-semibold text-purple-600 mb-4 uppercase tracking-wider">
        Nuestros Servicios
      </p>
      <h2 class="text-4xl sm:text-5xl lg:text-6xl font-bold text-black" style="font-family: var(--font-primary)">
        Soluciones <span class="bg-gradient-to-r from-purple-600 to-blue-600 bg-clip-text text-transparent" style="font-family: var(--font-secondary)">digitales</span> completas
      </h2>
      <p class="text-base sm:text-lg text-gray-600 mt-6 max-w-2xl mx-auto leading-relaxed">
        Todo lo que tu marca necesita para brillar en el mundo digital, bajo un mismo techo y con un equipo apasionado.
      </p>
    </div>

    <!-- Grid de Servicios -->
    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-8 sm:gap-10 lg:gap-12">
      <!-- Servicio 1: Producción de Contenido Audiovisual -->
      <div class="group p-8 sm:p-10 rounded-lg border border-gray-200 hover:border-purple-600 hover:shadow-lg transition-all duration-300 cursor-pointer">
        <div class="w-14 h-14 sm:w-16 sm:h-16 rounded-lg border-2 border-purple-600 flex items-center justify-center mb-6 group-hover:bg-purple-600 transition-colors duration-300">
          <Video className="w-7 h-7 sm:w-8 sm:h-8 text-purple-600 group-hover:text-white transition-colors duration-300" />
        </div>
        <h3 class="text-xl sm:text-2xl font-bold text-black mb-3">Producción de Contenido Audiovisual</h3>
        <p class="text-sm sm:text-base text-gray-600 leading-relaxed">
          Contenido profesional con storytelling auténtico, creado con equipos especializados y optimizado para generar engagement real en redes sociales.
        </p>
      </div>

      <!-- Servicio 2: Fotografía Profesional -->
      <div class="group p-8 sm:p-10 rounded-lg border border-gray-200 hover:border-blue-600 hover:shadow-lg transition-all duration-300 cursor-pointer">
        <div class="w-14 h-14 sm:w-16 sm:h-16 rounded-lg border-2 border-blue-600 flex items-center justify-center mb-6 group-hover:bg-blue-600 transition-colors duration-300">
          <Camera className="w-7 h-7 sm:w-8 sm:h-8 text-blue-600 group-hover:text-white transition-colors duration-300" />
        </div>
        <h3 class="text-xl sm:text-2xl font-bold text-black mb-3">Fotografía Profesional</h3>
        <p class="text-sm sm:text-base text-gray-600 leading-relaxed">
          Sesiones fotográficas profesionales para productos, marca personal y redes sociales. Cobertura visual que potencia tu identidad y destaca tu negocio.
        </p>
      </div>

      <!-- Servicio 3: Gestión de Redes Sociales -->
      <div class="group p-8 sm:p-10 rounded-lg border border-gray-200 hover:border-green-500 hover:shadow-lg transition-all duration-300 cursor-pointer">
        <div class="w-14 h-14 sm:w-16 sm:h-16 rounded-lg border-2 border-green-500 flex items-center justify-center mb-6 group-hover:bg-green-500 transition-colors duration-300">
          <Instagram className="w-7 h-7 sm:w-8 sm:h-8 text-green-500 group-hover:text-white transition-colors duration-300" />
        </div>
        <h3 class="text-xl sm:text-2xl font-bold text-black mb-3">Gestión de Redes Sociales</h3>
        <p class="text-sm sm:text-base text-gray-600 leading-relaxed">
          Estrategia, producción y gestión integral de tus redes sociales. Contenido que conecta, crea comunidad y genera resultados medibles para tu marca.
        </p>
      </div>

      <!-- Servicio 4: Branding e Identidad Visual -->
      <div class="group p-8 sm:p-10 rounded-lg border border-gray-200 hover:border-purple-600 hover:shadow-lg transition-all duration-300 cursor-pointer">
        <div class="w-14 h-14 sm:w-16 sm:h-16 rounded-lg border-2 border-purple-600 flex items-center justify-center mb-6 group-hover:bg-purple-600 transition-colors duration-300">
          <Palette className="w-7 h-7 sm:w-8 sm:h-8 text-purple-600 group-hover:text-white transition-colors duration-300" />
        </div>
        <h3 class="text-xl sm:text-2xl font-bold text-black mb-3">Branding e Identidad Visual</h3>
        <p class="text-sm sm:text-base text-gray-600 leading-relaxed">
          Creación de logo, identidad visual completa y manual de marca. Diseño gráfico profesional que refleja la esencia de tu negocio y genera conexión.
        </p>
      </div>

      <!-- Servicio 5: Asesorías Estratégicas -->
      <div class="group p-8 sm:p-10 rounded-lg border border-gray-200 hover:border-blue-600 hover:shadow-lg transition-all duration-300 cursor-pointer">
        <div class="w-14 h-14 sm:w-16 sm:h-16 rounded-lg border-2 border-blue-600 flex items-center justify-center mb-6 group-hover:bg-blue-600 transition-colors duration-300">
          <Lightbulb className="w-7 h-7 sm:w-8 sm:h-8 text-blue-600 group-hover:text-white transition-colors duration-300" />
        </div>
        <h3 class="text-xl sm:text-2xl font-bold text-black mb-3">Asesorías Estratégicas</h3>
        <p class="text-sm sm:text-base text-gray-600 leading-relaxed">
          Acompañamiento estratégico personalizado en marketing digital. Capacitación en producción, edición, storytelling y estrategias de venta para emprendedores y empresas.
        </p>
      </div>

      <!-- Servicio 6: Desarrollo Web -->
      <div class="group p-8 sm:p-10 rounded-lg border border-gray-200 hover:border-green-500 hover:shadow-lg transition-all duration-300 cursor-pointer">
        <div class="w-14 h-14 sm:w-16 sm:h-16 rounded-lg border-2 border-green-500 flex items-center justify-center mb-6 group-hover:bg-green-500 transition-colors duration-300">
          <Code className="w-7 h-7 sm:w-8 sm:h-8 text-green-500 group-hover:text-white transition-colors duration-300" />
        </div>
        <h3 class="text-xl sm:text-2xl font-bold text-black mb-3">Desarrollo Web</h3>
        <p class="text-sm sm:text-base text-gray-600 leading-relaxed">
          Experiencias digitales rápidas, seguras y diseñadas para convertir visitantes en clientes.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- CTA Button -->
    <div class="flex justify-center mt-16 sm:mt-20">
      <a href="/servicios" class="px-8 sm:px-10 py-3 sm:py-4 bg-gradient-to-r from-purple-600 to-blue-600 text-white font-semibold rounded-full hover:shadow-xl hover:scale-102 transition-all duration-300">
        Ver todos los servicios →
      </a>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
